longBusinessSummary: American Premium Water Corporation produces bottled water under the LALPINA brand name. The company was formerly known as Expert Group Inc. and changed its name to American Premium Water Corporation in October 2013. American Premium Water Corporation is based in Delray Beach, Florida.
